This product builds on the batched threshold encryption scheme and prototype by
the Commonware team:

  - simple-bte (https://github.com/commonwarexyz/simple-bte), dual-licensed
    Apache-2.0 / MIT. All pairing math, group FFTs, and the BTE scheme itself
    come from that crate, used here unmodified as a dependency.
  - "Batched Threshold Encryption: A Simple Construction", Guru Vamsi
    Policharla, IACR eprint 2026/760 (https://eprint.iacr.org/2026/760), and
    the accompanying write-up at https://commonware.xyz/blogs/bte.

